      "title": "用前必看丨卡卡提示",
      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "\n\n我是卡卡，这是一个FLUX的文生图工作流，可以看着每个部分的提示进行操作，欢迎加我好友，一起交流学习，微信：ZhiWenDesign\n\n所用到的模型及下载地址如下：\n\nschnell模型: https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/tree/main \n\ndev模型：https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev/tree/main\n本地存放位置为：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\unet\n\nhttps://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-3-medium/tree/main/text_encoders\n本地存放位置为：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\clip\n\nhttps://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev/tree/main/vae\n本地存放位置为：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\vae\n\nLoRA下载地址如下：\n\nhttps://civitai.com/models/661571"
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        62.144248962402344,
        244.050537109375
      ],
      "size": [
        424.3396301269531,
        138.6016387939453
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 13,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "卡卡提示",
      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "\n大模型输入节点，这里可以选择dev版、schnell版，最低加载内存为最低32G，低于32显存在加载的时候会报错，显存16G以上可以使用dev模型，低于16G使用schnell版。下载地址如下：\n\nschnell模型: https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/tree/main \n\ndev模型：https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev/tree/main\n \n本地存放位置为：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\unet"
      ],
      "color": "#233",
      "bgcolor": "#355"
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        53.97846984863281,
        642.223876953125
      ],
      "size": [
        424.21630859375,
        140.3336181640625
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 9,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "卡卡提示",
      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "\n  这里设置出土尺寸。默认比例1：1为1024*1024，可根据自己需要进行尺寸设置。\n  建议使用以下尺寸生成图像:\n  - 768 x 1344：竖版 (9:16)\n  - 915 x 1144：肖像 (4:5)\n  - 1024 x 1024：方形 1:1\n  - 1182 x 886：照片 (4:3)\n  - 1254 x 836：风景 (3:2)\n  - 1344 x 768：宽屏 (16:9)\n  - 1564 x 670：电影 (21:9)\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
